fferent propagation conditions and the number of\nantennas impact the secrecy performance are also provided.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 May 2020 19:01:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Jul 2020 01:15:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-02"}
