ult to the presence of\nmultiple star clusters with different ages in many of the regions. Upper limits\nof the dust-only 8 $\\mu$m emission as a function of age are provided.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 May 2020 19:13:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 Jun 2020 13:22:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-11"}
