cally in comparisons to previous calculations, data are\navailable in Excel (.xlsx) spreadsheets for each source. APPLICATIONS: The\ndatabase has applications in research, dosimetry, and brachytherapy planning.\nThis comprehensive update provides the medical physics community with more\naccurate TG-43 dose evaluation parameters, as well as fully-benchmarked source\nmodels distributed with egs_brachy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 May 2020 14:13:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-27"}
