 more jetty events in heavy-ion collisions\nrelative to that in p+p.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 May 2020 15:09:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 May 2020 00:30:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 27 Sep 2020 15:24:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-29"}
